## Pattern comparison

| Pattern | Consistency | Load | Best for |
|---------|-------------|------|----------|
| **Current (client `/api/me` + full sync)** | Medium | High | MVP |
| **Webhook primary + light `/api/me`** | High | Low | **Production default** |
| **JWT claims only (no getUser)** | Medium | Lowest | If claims have enough fields |
| **Sync only on signup (`user.created`)** | Medium | Low | If profile rarely changes |
| **Scheduled reconciliation job** | High | Batch | Backup for missed webhooks |

**Recommended hybrid (industry standard):**

```text
user.created / user.updated  →  Webhook  →  MySQL upsert
First app load after login     →  GET /api/me  →  read MySQL (create if missing fallback)
Profile display elsewhere      →  read MySQL only
```

