## What to keep vs change

| Keep | Change for production |
|------|------------------------|
| Clerk on frontend + Express verify JWT | Add webhooks as **source of truth** for writes |
| `clerk_id` as stable key | Make `/api/me` **read-first**, sync-on-miss |
| `requireApiAuth` + Bearer token | Add cross-tab dedup + retry on client |
| UNIQUE `clerk_id` | Conditional UPDATE or webhook-only updates |
| `ClerkUserSync` as safety net | Demote to fallback, not primary writer |

